    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for reliable transportation on a budget or a light project. The engine runs and the car is drivable, though it does show its age with some noticeable cosmetic wear, including minor dents and interior staining. While it has been consistently driven, it will likely need some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to keep it in peak operating shape. It\u2019s an honest car that reflects its years on the road, offering a functional experience for a fair price.",
