    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am selling my absolute favorite ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a champ. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super dependable for all my trips. If you're looking for a car that\u2019s been well-loved and is ready to hit the road with its next owner, this is definitely the one for you! I'm happy to chat and answer any questions you have\u2014let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 32500.0,
