      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six. This unit boasts crisp throttle response via its factory ITBs and delivers power through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement\u2014critical for this chassis. The suspension has been refreshed with Bilstein B6 dampers, maintaining the factory geometry while sharpening turn-in. While showing minor patina consistent with its mileage, the engine pulls strongly to its 8,000 RPM redline. A true driver\u2019s specimen for the enthusiast who prioritizes longitudinal dynamics and chassis feedback.",
